ce:section.ce:para:
To evaluated the cytocompatibility of Rapa-CDs, Rapa-CDs with different concentrations in the medium was characterized by cell counting kit-8 (CCK-8) method at 24 and 48 h. The results exhibit the cellular viability is almost 100 % at 0–400 μg/mL Rapa-CDs, presenting excellent biocompatibility (
                           Fig. S3
                        ).
